# Bitmap - KX Dashboards

Original URL: https://code.kx.com/dashboards/bitmap/

# Bitmap

![Screenshot](../img/bitmap/bitmap.jpg)

Renders bitmap images in the dashboard.

## Settings

![Screenshot](../img/bitmap/bitmapmenu.png)

_Name_

    A name for the component provided by the user. 
_Data Source_

    Details of the bitmap image are stored in a query; included are [view state parameters](../viewstateparameters/) for title, height and width of image. Axes labels should be included a part of query if required. 
    ![Screenshot](../img/bitmap/datasourcebitmap.jpg)
     [Data sources](../datasources/)
_Width_

    Auto assigned [view state parameter](../viewstateparameters/) storing bitmap image width in pixels. Value updates on browser resize. 
_Height_

    Auto assigned [view state parameter](../viewstateparameters/) storing bitmap image height in pixels. Value updates on browser resize. 

